{"word":"ἀναμίγνυμι","slug":"ἀναμίγνυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναμίγνυμι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to mix up, mix together</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be mixed</i> with others, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic: <i>to have intercourse</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li250'><b>B. </b><el>ἀναμίσγω</el>, <a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> and ionic for <el>ἀναμίγνυμι</el>, only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to mix</i> one thing <i>with</i> another, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to have intercourse</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}